description: The DSM-5 Exam skill provides you with a review of all of the disorders in the DSM-5, including diagnostic features, prevalence, disorder development, and risk factors associated with certain disorders. Assessment and treatment recommendations are also discussed.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell dsm five exam to talk to me about Schizophrenia
Alexa, tell dsm five exam to talk to me about autism
